    <h1>Climbing Kilimanjaro With Kids: Minimum Age, Success Rates, and What Families Need to Know</h1>
    <p>Tanzania National Parks' 10-year minimum, the realistic minimum age for summiting, recommended routes for families, and what to know about climbing Kilimanjaro with children from the team that has guided many family expeditions.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
